        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-04-30T17:30:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-04-30T17:30:00-05:00" n="534" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d534">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">831.6363/4–3048: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Venezuela</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Carrigan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret   us urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-04-30T18:00:00-04:30">April 30, 1948—6 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>334. Creole, Meneg and Shell are presently coordinating their views in close and
                    continuous collaboration with Embassy and four attachés. Our joint task is to
                    recommend detailed plans for implementing general program outlined <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 330 April 29<note n="1" xml:id="d534fn1">Not printed.</note> which will afford maximum protection possible against
                    sabotage and at same time minimize risk of government opposition or political
                    repercussions which might defeat our whole purpose and prejudice position of the
                    companies. …</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Carrigan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
